summary: 

Dan and Phil were both struggling with their own demons, and their relationship was falling apart. They were going through the worst time of their lives, and things between them ending seemed like the only possible way out… wasn’t it?

title: welcome to my blog!!
body:
hi my names lexi and i have a love for writing!! i’ve had a couple writing blogs in the past but none of them felt right to me so i decided to make a new one.

requests are open for;

- the umbrella academy 

- dan and phil

characters i’ll write for;

- five, vanya, diego, allison, klaus, ben

characters i won’t write for;

- luther, pogo, grace, reginald

prompts;

list two ten dialogue prompts

list three soft sentence starters

you don’t have to use the prompts!! you can also send me your own ideas as well!!
